Sentencas: Cubic perovskite-type (Ba0.6Sr0.4)(1-x)LaxCo0.85Ti0.15O3-delta (BSLCT, 0 < x < 0.2) materials were synthesized and evaluated as cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) based on Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-delta (GDC).
Titulo: Characterization and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.6Sr0.4)1-xLaxCo0.85Ti0.15O3 as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The influence of La-doping on the lattice structure, electrical conductivity, chemical compatibility with electrolyte GDC, and cathode performance of BSLCTs were studied.
Titulo: Characterization and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.6Sr0.4)1-xLaxCo0.85Ti0.15O3 as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
